Here's a link to a news article in which scientists have found the gay gene in fruit flies. Literally. Manipulating this gene, and nothing else in the genes or environment, can cause a fruit fly to court and mate with the same or opposite sex.  http://www.foxnews.com/story/0  ,2933,316316,00.html